Has everybody responded to commissioners?

708
01:11:36,010 --> 01:11:37,571
Anything else to say?

709
01:11:43,736 --> 01:11:59,427
You all received the information with all the upcoming events this month, hoping to see as many of you as possible at the flag raising ceremony for Juneteenth on Thursday the 15th, that's tomorrow.

710
01:12:00,268 --> 01:12:05,652
West Medford Community Centre is hosting a full ceremony

711
01:12:06,338 --> 01:12:31,971
eat with drums and vendors and that is happening on the 17th and it starts at 12 o'clock and the city's hosting its big pride festival and that is happening on the 25th and that will include bands, DJ, vendors,

712
01:12:33,352 --> 01:12:36,235
A whole slew of things.

713
01:12:36,535 --> 01:12:40,479
So just wanted to make sure you received that.

714
01:12:42,060 --> 01:12:47,365
And that concludes everything that we have thus far on the agenda.

715
01:12:47,425 --> 01:12:52,790
So I'm going to turn it over for public participation because it's now 6.50.

716
01:12:54,792 --> 01:12:55,893
Go ahead, please, Judy.

717
01:12:58,976 --> 01:13:13,360
Yes, I want to apologize for momentarily losing my temper, but, you know, I think it's extremely disrespectful that, you know, I am the only public person here and that I have not had an opportunity to introduce myself.

718
01:13:13,780 --> 01:13:18,341
And I also think it was very inappropriate not to introduce the candidates at the beginning.

719
