And also, I think if you want the commission to be taken seriously and to take yourself seriously, you should capitalize commission and commissioners.

734
01:14:59,121 --> 01:15:00,381
You also have a typo.

735
01:15:02,280 --> 01:15:04,061
that was just introduced tonight.

736
01:15:04,501 --> 01:15:10,404
And I do think the second and third paragraphs are quite good.

737
01:15:10,524 --> 01:15:11,665
I think they're excellent.

738
01:15:12,485 --> 01:15:16,627
So I've saved all my comments and that's all I have to say.

739
