01:16:25,164 --> 01:16:32,609
Mayor was going to come on and issue thanks, but it seems as though... I'm here.

752
01:16:35,411 --> 01:16:36,092
I made it.

753
01:16:36,872 --> 01:16:37,413
I made it.

754
01:16:38,093 --> 01:16:41,035
I had a double committee meeting.

