01:16:41,075 --> 01:16:44,317
My apologies, I would have liked to have been on at the beginning.

756
01:16:45,532 --> 01:16:48,094
especially since Francis told me what time it started.

757
01:16:48,174 --> 01:16:52,617
So my apologies that I'm a little bit late and I'm glad I caught you before y'all got off.

